<ui:UXML xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:ui="UnityEngine.UIElements" xmlns:uie="UnityEditor.UIElements" noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../UIElementsSchema/UIElements.xsd" editor-extension-mode="False">
    <Style src="project://database/Assets/Scripts/MainTheme.uss?fileID=7433441132597879392&guid=e74b56d351668304195e8e784c0c0a4a&type=3#MainTheme"/>
    <ui:VisualElement name="menu-bar" style="flex-grow: 0; background-color: rgb(37, 37, 38); height: 60px; align-items: stretch; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center;">

        <ui:VisualElement name="graph-panel" style="flex-grow: 1; align-self: stretch; flex-direction: column-reverse;"/>
